data.description: Your perfect Florida retreat awaits! You will feel at home from the moment you approach the front porch where you can enjoy your morning coffee and embrace the laid-back lifestyle. Notice the NEWER ROOF that is only four years old. This well-maintained split floorplan   3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2 car garage home built by Windemere is a showcase of modern elegance with a touch of warmth. Upon entering the home, you will begin to experience the many upgrades including NEW luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, 5” baseboards, crown molding in some areas, and updated light fixtures. The open floor plan features cathedral ceilings, freshly painted interior and an abundance of natural sunlight. The heart of the home, the kitchen, has been tastefully UPDATED with CUSTOM solid wood cabinetry with soft close hinges, and pull-out cabinet drawers, quartz countertops, oversized island, tile backsplash, deep drop-in sink with modern fixture. The large island is multi-functional and offers plenty of storage, ample countertop space and breakfast bar that opens to the great room. The microwave is brand new, and the other stainless-steel appliances are less than five years old. The owners will enjoy their privacy as the main En-suite offers a walk-in shower, and a large walk-in closet is on one side of the home while the two guest bedrooms with a shared bathroom are on the opposite side of the home. Both bathrooms have UPDATED vanities, quartz countertops, mirrors and lighting. There is also an enclosed sunroom with french doors leading out to the fenced back yard where you can enjoy the Florida weather in your private outdoor space. Whether you're sipping morning coffee or hosting a BBQ, relaxing by the firepit with family, this is your personal haven. This home is NOT in a flood zone and NO HOA’s. Located just minutes from I-75 and Tamiami Trail. Convenient to Florida’s best beaches, golf, public boat ramps, shopping, restaurants, entertainment, nature trails, and fishing. Just a short drive to the CoolToday Park Stadium (home to the Atlanta Braves Spring Training Camp) Wellen Park, North Port Aquatic Center, Morgan Family Center and the famous Warm Mineral Springs. Your charming Florida home is ready to welcome you. Don't miss the chance to own this piece of paradise. Schedule a showing today!
